E4Plus1.uk.description: Charlie's: Gordon Ramsay visits Italian bistro Charlie's, where the pasta's soggy, the lasagne's a liability and the chef can't even cook a meatball. (S5 Ep10) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: An unexpected arrival at the retreat leads to a showdown. And as a marital breakdown spirals, everyone's caught in the crossfire at an explosive dinner party. (S10 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Whistler's Father: Maggie reveals a hidden talent, which Grampa tries to exploit. Marge gets a job as a decorator for the mob. (S29 Ep3/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Mr. Lisa's Opus: In her Harvard application, 18-year-old Lisa recounts the story of her childhood - including the time when Marge planned to leave Homer... (S29 Ep8/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The First Pitch Insufficiency: Howard's nervous when NASA ask him to throw the first pitch at a baseball game. Sheldon claims his and Amy's relationship is the best in the gang. (S8 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Hook-Up Reverberation: Raj's honesty about his past comes back to haunt him when his girlfriend Emily gives Penny the cold shoulder. The guys consider an investment. (S8 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Baby on Board: Trying to adopt another child has been an emotional roller coaster for Mitch and Cam. They bring Gloria in as translator, leaving Jay and Manny to look after Lily. (S3 Ep24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bringing Up Baby: Jay makes it clear that he wants to keep his birthday as low-key as possible. (S4 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Gyroscopic Collapse: Amy is offered a fellowship at Princeton, Raj makes new living arrangements, and the guys' gyroscope project spins out of control. (S10 Ep23/24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Long Distance Dissonance: The gang worry when Sheldon's former admirer, Dr Ramona Nowitzki, turns up while Amy is away working at Princeton. (S10 Ep24/24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Proposal Proposal: Amy must decide whether or not to marry Sheldon and gives him an answer to his proposal. Howard and Bernadette struggle with some unexpected news. (S11 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Retraction Reaction: Leonard angers the university during an embarrassing interview. Amy and Bernadette must hide their success from Sheldon and Howard. (S11 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Captain Kim: A new captain at the Nine-Nine attempts to ingratiate herself with Jake and the squad by inviting them over to her house for a dinner party. (S7 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pimemento: Adrian Pimento shows up unexpectedly, claiming that someone's trying to kill him, and asking for Jake and Charles' help. But he keeps losing his memory... (S7 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Undercover Burns: Mr Burns goes undercover to see what the employees really think of him, and becomes their friends - to Smithers' alarm... (S32 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Now Museum, Now You Don't: Lisa explores the wonders of western art. She becomes Lisanardo, and Bart turns into a French impressionist. (S32 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: An unexpected arrival at the retreat leads to a showdown. And as a marital breakdown spirals, everyone's caught in the crossfire at an explosive dinner party. (S10 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Tenant Disassociation: Leonard competes with Sheldon to become president of the tenants' association. Howard and Raj find a drone in the back garden. (S11 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Reclusive Potential: A brilliant scientist invites Sheldon to his isolated cabin, and Leonard, Raj and Howard go along for the trip. (S11 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Ice Cream of Margie (With the Light Blue Hair): Marge, feeling overshadowed by Homer's new career selling ice cream, starts creating ice lolly stick sculptures. (S18 Ep7/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Haw-Hawed Couple: Bart becomes Nelson's best friend when Marge makes him go to his birthday party. Which means no one can mess with Bart. But there are downsides too... (S18 Ep8/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: The village reels from the explosive events of Hollyoaks' anniversary week as residents face the emotional fallout - with hearts broken, loyalties tested and unlikely alliances formed.

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Hollyoaks Does Come Dine...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...with Me: Brand new series: To mark 30 years of the soap, Hollyoaks stars compete for charity. Will McQueen matriarch Nicole Barber-Lane's tropical night be a slice of paradise? (Ep1/5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Supercruising: Life at Sea
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Caribbean cruisers anchor in the Dominican Republic for chocolate making, but it's the onboard 'Dressy Night' that's the real icing on the cake with a triumphant taste explosion. (Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: It's Commitment Ceremony time and some couples reap the rewards from their time away. But for others, turmoil takes hold... is one marriage beyond repair? (S10 Ep24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Made in Chelsea
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Beks and Sam Prince get cosy in the Cotswolds, but have they crossed a line? Livvy's torn between Kit and Chuggs. Sam Vanderpump is rocked by life-changing news. (S30 Ep7)
